<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <meta name="description" content="Spark N Snack — curated boxes to spark joy and faith, created by Gracie & Sabreana. Inspiring creative growth and fun connections.">
    <title>Spark N Snack | Inspire. Create. Connect.</title>
    <link rel="icon" href="https://via.placeholder.com/64" type="image/jpeg">
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary-color: #ff7f50;
            --secondary-color: #fff3e6;
            --text-color: #333;
            --bg-color: #f9f9f9;
            --white: #ffffff;
            --shadow: 0 4px 15px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            --transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        body {
            font-family: 'Poppins', sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            background-color: var(--bg-color);
            color: var(--text-color);
            line-height: 1.6;
        }
        header {
            background-color: var(--primary-color);
            color: var(--white);
            text-align: center;
            padding: 3rem 0;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow);
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }
        header::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: -50px;
            left: 0;
            width: 100%;
            height: 100px;
            background: var(--bg-color);
            transform: skewY(-2deg);
        }
        header img {
            max-width: 180px;
            height: auto;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            border-radius: 50%;
            border: 6px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.3);
            background: white;
            padding: 5px;
            box-shadow: 0 10px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.15);
        }
        header h1 {
            margin: 0;
            font-size: 3rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            letter-spacing: 2px;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 1;
        }
        nav {
            margin-top: 1rem;
        }
        .nav-link {
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            border-bottom: 2px solid transparent;
            transition: var(--transition);
        }
        .nav-link:hover {
            border-bottom-color: white;
            opacity: 0.9;
        }
        .container {
            width: 90%;
            max-width: 1100px;
            margin: 4rem auto;
            padding: 0 1rem;
            position: relative;
            z-index: 2;
        }
        .description {
            background: var(--white);
            padding: 3rem;
            margin: 2rem 0;
            border-top: 8px solid var(--primary-color);
            border-radius: 12px;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow);
        }
        .description h2 {
            margin-top: 0;
            color: var(--primary-color);
            font-size: 2rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
        }
        .description p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
        }
        .value-proposition {
            background-color: var(--secondary-color);
            padding: 4rem;
            border-radius: 16px;
            text-align: center;
            border-left: 8px solid var(--primary-color);
            box-shadow: var(--shadow);
            margin-bottom: 4rem;
        }
        .value-proposition h2 {
            color: var(--primary-color);
            font-size: 2.2rem;
            margin-bottom: 2rem;
        }
        .value-proposition ul {
            list-style: none;
            padding: 0;
            text-align: left;
            display: inline-block;
            max-width: 800px;
        }
        .value-proposition li {
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            position: relative;
            padding-left: 2.5rem;
        }
        .value-proposition li::before {
            content: '★';
            color: var(--primary-color);
            position: absolute;
            left: 0;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            line-height: 1.2;
        }
        .product-showcase {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 2.5rem;
            padding: 1rem 0;
            margin-bottom: 4rem;
        }
        .product {
            background: var(--white);
            padding: 2rem;
            border-radius: 16px;
            text-align: center;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow);
            transition: var(--transition);
            border-bottom: 5px solid transparent;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: inherit;
        }
        .product img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 200px;
            object-fit: cover;
            border-radius: 12px;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            background-color: #eee;
        }
        .product:hover {
            transform: translateY(-10px);
            border-bottom: 5px solid var(--primary-color);
        }
        .product h3 {
            color: var(--primary-color);
            margin-top: 0;
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        .subscription-form {
            background: var(--white);
            padding: 4rem;
            border-radius: 16px;
            box-shadow: var(--shadow);
            margin-bottom: 4rem;
        }
        .subscription-form h2 {
            text-align: center;
            color: var(--primary-color);
            margin-bottom: 2.5rem;
            font-size: 2.2rem;
        }
        .form-group {
            margin-bottom: 1.8rem;
        }
        .form-group label {
            display: block;
            margin-bottom: 0.6rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            color: #555;
        }
        .subscription-form input {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 1rem;
            border: 2px solid #eee;
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-family: inherit;
            font-size: 1rem;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            transition: var(--transition);
        }
        .subscription-form input:focus {
            outline: none;
            border-color: var(--primary-color);
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(255, 127, 80, 0.1);
        }
        .subscription-form button {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 1.2rem;
            background-color: var(--primary-color);
            color: var(--white);
            border: none;
            border-radius: 10px;
            font-size: 1.2rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            cursor: pointer;
            transition: var(--transition);
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(255, 127, 80, 0.3);
            margin-top: 1rem;
        }
        .subscription-form button:hover {
            background-color: #e66e40;
            transform: translateY(-2px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 20px rgba(255, 127, 80, 0.4);
        }
        footer {
            text-align: center;
            padding: 4rem 0;
            background: #333;
            color: #eee;
        }
        footer p {
            margin: 0;
        }
        .back-link {
            display: inline-block;
            margin-top: 2rem;
            color: var(--primary-color);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-weight: 600;
            border-bottom: 2px solid transparent;
            transition: var(--transition);
        }
        .back-link:hover {
            border-bottom-color: var(--primary-color);
        }
        @media (max-width: 768px) {
            header h1 { font-size: 2.2rem; }
            .description, .subscription-form { padding: 2rem; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/180" alt="Spark N Snack Logo">
        <h1>Spark N Snack</h1>
        <nav>
            <a href="#pricing" class="nav-link">View Pricing</a>
        </nav>
    </header>
    <div class="container">
        <section class="description">
            <h2>About Spark N Snack</h2>
            <p>
                At <strong>Spark N Snack</strong>, we believe in sparking joy and creativity in every moment! 
                Founded by <strong>Gracie and Sabreana</strong>, our mission is to deliver thoughtfully curated subscription boxes 
                that inspire, uplift, and bring fun into everyday life. Each box is designed to reflect our playful spirit, 
                faith, and commitment to personal growth. Join us on a journey of discovery, delight, and meaningful connections!
            </p>
        </section>

        <section class="product-showcase">
            <div class="product">
                <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/300x200" alt="The Spark Box">
                <h3>The Spark Box</h3>
                <p>Ignite your creativity with DIY projects, journaling prompts, and inspirational tools designed to help you shine.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="product">
                <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/300x200" alt="The Spirit Box">
                <h3>The Spirit Box</h3>
                <p>Nurture your soul with devotionals, prayer journals, and uplifting messages for spiritual growth.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="product">
                <img src="https://via.placeholder.com/300x200" alt="The Combo Delight">
                <h3>The Combo Delight</h3>
                <p>The best of both worlds! Creative sparks and spiritual nourishment in one package. Includes exclusive behind-the-scenes videos of our story.</p>
            </div>
        </section>

        <section class="value-proposition">
            <h2>Why Join the Spark N Snack Community?</h2>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>Curated with Purpose:</strong> Every item is hand-picked by Gracie & Sabreana to bring you joy.</li>
                <li><strong>Faith & Fun Combined:</strong> We bridge the gap between spiritual growth and creative expression.</li>
                <li><strong>Exclusive Community Access:</strong> Join a network of like-minded women supporting each other.</li>
                <li><strong>Zero Risk:</strong> Skip a month or cancel anytime. Satisfaction guaranteed!</li>
            </ul>
        </section>

        <section class="subscription-form">
            <h2>Start Your Journey</h2>
            <form name="subscription" method="POST" data-netlify="true" netlify-honeypot="bot-field">
                <input type="hidden" name="form-name" value="subscription" />
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="name">Name</label>
                    <input type="text" id="name" name="name" placeholder="Your full name" required>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="email">Email</label>
                    <input type="email" id="email" name="email" placeholder="your@email.com" required>
                </div>
                <div class="form-group">
                    <label for="address">Shipping Address</label>
                    <input type="text" id="address" name="address" placeholder="123 Joy St, Happiness, CA" required>
                </div>
                <button type="submit">Subscribe Now</button>
            </form>
        </section>
    </div>

    <footer>
        <p>&copy; 2026 Spark N Snack. Created with joy by Gracie and Sabreana.</p>
    </footer>
</body>
</html>
